1. [P0] Fix 1 cleanup would break live help drawer consumers — `HELP_PREVIEW_LIMIT` is still read at `x.jsx:2701`, `x.jsx:4935`, and `x.jsx:5027`, and `HELP_CHIPS` is still iterated at `x.jsx:5102`. The task requires both constants to be removed while also forbidding JSX changes, so following the prompt literally would leave unresolved identifiers in active code. FIX: either keep both constants until the JSX phase, or include the four consumer updates in this task.
2. [P1] Fix 1 cannot actually switch the drawer to the six-button preset set in this revision — the visible grid is hardcoded inline at `x.jsx:5048-5054` to `call_waiter`, `bill`, `napkins`, and `menu`. Updating `HELP_REQUEST_TYPES` / `HELP_CARD_LABELS` alone will not surface `plate`, `utensils`, or `clear_table`, and legacy `menu` will remain visible. FIX: move the grid to config-driven rendering or let the companion JSX task update the preset card list.
3. [P1] Fix 1 is still missing the new type whitelist in restore/sync logic — `HELP_REQUEST_TYPES` at `x.jsx:1796` and `nonOtherTypes` at `x.jsx:2130` still exclude `plate`, `utensils`, and `clear_table`, while the ServiceRequest feed is filtered through that set at `x.jsx:2053` and `x.jsx:2061`. New SOS requests of those types would be dropped during polling/restore. FIX: extend both whitelists to include the three new preset types while keeping `menu` legacy-only.
4. [P1] Fix 2 urgency thresholds/helpers are absent — there is no `HELP_URGENCY_THRESHOLDS`, `HELP_URGENCY_GROUP`, `getHelpUrgency`, or `getHelpTimerStr`, and current ticket copy still comes from the generic wait label at `x.jsx:2554-2558`. That leaves no code path for the requested amber/red urgency escalation or compact timer formatting. FIX: add the two `useMemo` maps after `HELP_COOLDOWN_SECONDS` and add both `useCallback` helpers before render.
5. [P1] Fix 4 i18n coverage is still on the legacy help vocabulary — the EN block at `x.jsx:525-553` still exposes `help.bill`, `help.menu`, `help.comment_placeholder_other`, and lacks the new v6.0 keys (`help.get_bill`, `help.plate`, `help.utensils`, `help.clear_table`, all short-label keys, `help.subtitle_choose`, `help.table_default`, `help.cancel_*`, `help.other_request_link`, `help.other_placeholder`, `help.send_btn`). The RU block at `x.jsx:592-620` still has the long `help.get_bill` copy and is missing `help.plate`, `help.utensils`, `help.clear_table`, the short-label keys, `help.sent_suffix`, and `help.undo`. FIX: add the missing EN/RU fallback keys and shorten RU `help.get_bill` to `Счёт` as specified, without duplicating keys that already exist correctly.

